{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":170,"question":"最好在30岁之前能晋升到管理岗位。如果一直停留在基层岗位上，和职场新人相比精力体力上不占优势，工资成本又高很多，很有可能被公司裁掉。<br/><br/>这个分析属于滑坡谬误吗?","type":1,"analysis":"精力体力不占优势、工资成本高是并列因素，没有一系列的因果关系，因此不属于滑坡谬误","pic":null,"difficulty":2,"knowledgeId":13,"sceneId":1,"del":true,"problemId":5,"sequence":15,"example":false,"practiceUid":"T005B006B003X01015","score":30,"choiceList":[{"id":492,"questionId":170,"subject":"属于","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":493,"questionId":170,"subject":"不属于","sequence":2,"isRight":true,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":676,"warmupPracticeId":170,"repliedId":null,"comment":"虽然选对了，但是原因不同。没有察觉这些因素是并列而非阶梯（因果），而且觉得确实是这样的。虽然这个推导得出的结论不一定是“30岁前要升到管理岗位”，但如果一直在基层，要么是能力不足以胜任，要么是该公司竞争激烈，确实是面临着被淘汰的风险。我是出于这个角度觉得这不属于滑坡谬误。","openid":null,"addTime":1488781132000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Yanae Yang","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WUxgnmxEpgcwKia4vSaVZr6Oyx2wYIgoMAk7cUOb6WN5T3vPfq7c4AdwgTmtGH75t6NspLErm5UhaZIYRRg6oTH/0","discussTime":"2017-03-06"},{"id":473,"warmupPracticeId":170,"repliedId":348,"comment":"我也是啊！低价失误","openid":null,"addTime":1488417527000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"审题不清疏忽大意！","del":0,"repliedName":"Juvae","name":"施伟","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","discussTime":"2017-03-02"},{"id":348,"warmupPracticeId":170,"repliedId":null,"comment":"审题不清疏忽大意！","openid":null,"addTime":1488121752000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Juvae","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoO92kqn9zYibHA0icSRJB8q67kFhVGDz9UJ3YIOsTr2zWFh6iaIycONL49U7HgkfokASzcIeLjQq9dO/0","discussTime":"2017-02-26"},{"id":239,"warmupPracticeId":170,"repliedId":null,"comment":"表达完原因后用的是很可能，没有说必然性。","openid":null,"addTime":1487883863000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Wxiaoying","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay0GlHKN7b680wX42XIHPQ3oZnLcBZHnWuGaW6e1AfPkic1MLLL7TN20tJsojvQevG0ah2btwp9ur3/0","discussTime":"2017-02-24"},{"id":5,"warmupPracticeId":170,"repliedId":null,"comment":"之前对于滑坡谬误只关注了因果联系里面的必然性和偶然性，这道题则提醒了另一个方面，滑坡理论需要是一系列连续的因果联系，很赞!","openid":null,"addTime":1487122785000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"程然","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibeXpgwkiaTloWbvWZibHU3ulLlIhhE6iaIiazJaXkXaYkTTbdwvhdOM7cvxOoQpCxud7DYns8icjZDZ7w/0","discussTime":"2017-02-15"}],"choice":null,"knowledge":{"id":13,"knowledge":"滑坡谬误","step":"识别谬误：中难度","analysis":"“现在不好好学习，长大找不到好工作，以后就要捡破烂”，你小时候有被家长这样“教育”过吗?\n不好的结果没那么容易就发生，破解这类滑坡谬误，才能不再轻易被套路。","means":"滑坡谬误：即不合理地使用连串的因果关系，将“可能性”转化为“必然性”，从而得到不合理的结论。\n\n如何破解滑坡谬误：\n在别人抛出一连串推论时，要求对方描述清楚，这个结果到底如何产生，或者自己举出反例，有什么理由让这个推论不成立。","keynote":"可以通过攻击“必然关系”破解滑坡谬误","pic":null,"audio":"http://www.iqycamp.com/audio/rise_k13.m4a","appear":0,"example":null}}]},"code":200}
